title: 2024 Multidisciplinary Specialty Conference
text:
Brought you by Taiwan Medical Mission
2024 Multidisciplinary Specialty Conference (2024MSC) Date: Saturday, 11 May, 2024 Time: 09:00 AM - 12:30 PM Venue: Conference Hall, Hargeisa Group Hospital, Hargeisa, Somaliland
This year, We have 3 topics:

Taiwan Cares: Somaliland Dengue Control Project
Esophageal cancer, Hepatoma, and Digital pathology in Somaliland
Orthopedic training in HGH and Taipei Municipal Wanfang Hospital
